imdb.plot outline: "Comedy with Karsten" presenter Christian Meyer shows the each day highlights of the comedy festival "Humor Zone Dresden". Over 50 artists like Michael Mitter Meier, Rainald Grebe, Dietmar Wischmeyer,Willy Astor, Özcan Caesar, Torsten Sträter, Enissa Amani, Ulan Bator and, Christin Henkel and Kay Ray, present their programs on four days and seven stages. At the end of the show series is a great closing Gala, presented by Olaf Schubert. Karel Gott, appears as musical special guest.
